  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.12.6\n\n### What happened?\n\nWebSocket server does not accept the array of RPC messages. The message is not valid:\r\n\r\n[`handleWs` handler.ts#L91](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/654e7cd44a0f1229a44538f73584c538961a117e/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/hardhat-network/jsonrpc/handler.ts#L91)\r\n\r\nThough the HTTP server accepts arrays: [`handleHttp` handler.ts#L41](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/654e7cd44a0f1229a44538f73584c538961a117e/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/hardhat-network/jsonrpc/handler.ts#L41)\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\nSend a message to `ws://127.0.0.1:8545`\r\n\r\n```json\r\n[\r\n    {\r\n        \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n        \"id\": 17,\r\n        \"method\": \"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\r\n        \"params\": [\r\n            \"0x188f8a6a69535e9e1e5fd8a9ad844325f4f01157e039035f0f16de14a97a3b69\"\r\n        ]\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n        \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n        \"id\": 18,\r\n        \"method\": \"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\r\n        \"params\": [\r\n            \"0x33b1a6378404ab21d213ff2d9cbe660417fdacb990de054651637537f663ceb6\"\r\n        ]\r\n    }\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\n> Same body requests to `POST https://127.0.0.1:8545` works.\n\n### Search terms\n\nBatchRequest",
